
Package: ArthropodMonitoringAnalysis
Title: Statistical Analysis for Integrated Arthropod Monitoring Pipeline
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Victor", "Scharnhorst",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "victor.scharnhorst@example.com")
Description: R analysis scripts and statistical models for arthropod biodiversity
    monitoring data. This package contains the analysis code for the publication
    "Cheaper, Faster, More Comprehensive: AI-based image analysis pipeline for
    biodiversity surveys" submitted to Current Biology.
License: MIT + file ../LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
